    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is paired with a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-Variable Lock differential. This unit is in concours-level condition, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and subframe reinforcement to ensure peak torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains stock, featuring MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for precise lateral grip. The exterior showcases original paint with zero oxidation, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A mechanically flawless example of BMW\u2019s peak engineering era, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
